bilingual.source: W. S. People in this stage are overly interested in their idols' lives and movements.
bilingual.target: 他们过度地迷恋明星的个人生活，乃至明星的一举一动。

bilingual.source: His reaction to the news was overly melodramatic.
bilingual.target: 他对这条消息的反应过于夸张。

bilingual.source: His approach to the problem was overly reductive.
bilingual.target: 他对问题的处理方式过于简化的。

bilingual.source: The company's sales forecasts were overly optimistic.
bilingual.target: 公司的销售预测过于乐观。

bilingual.source: His speech was criticized as being overly masturbatory.
bilingual.target: 他的演讲被批评为过于自我满足。

bilingual.source: The overly sentimental movie started to cloy the audience.
bilingual.target: 过于感伤的电影开始使人感到腻烦观众。

bilingual.source: He might overcompensate for his guilt by being overly generous.
bilingual.target: 他可能会通过过度慷慨来过度补偿他的内疚。

bilingual.source: Parents should not overly interfere with their children's choices.
bilingual.target: 父母不应该过多干涉孩子的选择。

bilingual.source: Sometimes, being overly smart can make you too clever for your own good.
bilingual.target: 有时候，过于聪明会让你聪明反被聪明误。

bilingual.source: He tends to overcompensate for his lack of confidence by being overly aggressive.
bilingual.target: 他倾向于通过过度的攻击性来过度补偿他缺乏自信的问题。

yingyinNormal.en: Serena, as usual, you're being overly dramatic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑟琳娜，你还是老样子，太夸张了。

yingyinNormal.en: I was not panicked, and I am not overly attached to Leonard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有害怕，我也不依赖莱纳德。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, when I've been drinking, sometimes I tend to get overly friendly, and I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喝了酒以后，有时候会变得太热情，对不起。

yingyinNormal.en: Penny laid into me, too. Apparently, I'm overly fixated on premium Swiss chocolate bars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮也把我骂了一顿。显然，我过分专注在优质的瑞士巧克力棒上。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, let's see, she attempted to open her apartment with her car key because her face is overly Midwestern.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，她尝试用车钥匙来开门，因为她的脸太中西部化了。

yingyinNormal.en: Not much. Although, I can be faulted for being overly fond of Koala bears. I don't know what it is, when they start munching on eucalyptus, I just melt inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没大有，当然，要说缺点的话，我就是太过于喜欢考拉熊了。我也不知道怎么回事，每当看到它们在桉树上大嚼特嚼时，我整个人都融化了。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, you do it when the wok's off, because the coriander, you see, is just going to wilt, and I don't want it to be overly cooked, I just want it to soften down.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，关火后再加。因为香菜容易打蔫，我不想把香菜煮过头，只想让它们稍稍软一点。

yingyinNormal.en: He probably feels that it's doubtful that his mother will be overly impressed with his dating a woman whose most significant achievement is memorizing the Cheesecake Factory menu.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他可能是觉得他妈妈很难认同他跟一个生平最高成就就是背下芝士蛋糕工厂菜单的女人约会。

yingyinNormal.en: He didn't look tentative. He didn't look overly concerned. He looked like, "dude, I'm about to go do it. "if they cut me, they cut me. "if I don't never play another NBA game, so be it. I'm going to play like Jeremy Lin can play."
yingyinNormal.zh: 他看起来没有犹豫也没有过于忧虑，他看起来就像在说，“我要放手一搏了” 如果他们裁了我就裁吧，就算我再也不能在NBA打球也无所谓了，我要让你们看看真正的林书豪是怎么打球的
